---
title: AskSurgeons — Blog
description: "Helpful articles, surgeon guides and patient resources."
---
{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}
{% block content %}
<section class="hero">
  <h1>AskSurgeons — clear surgical guidance</h1>
  <p>Read our articles. When ready, <a href="https://app.asksurgeons.com" target="_blank">book an appointment</a>.</p>
</section>

<section id="blog" class="posts">
  <h2>Latest posts</h2>
  <ul>
    {% for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
    <li>
      <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
      <small>{{ post.date | dateReadable }}</small>
    </li>
    {% else %}
    <li>No posts yet</li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>
{% endblock %}
